description:
Logstash is a tool for managing events and logs. You can use it to cppollect logs, parse them, and store them for later use (like, for searching). 
    This package installs logstash contrib plugins, as starting logstash 1.4.0 many plugins moved out of the main logstash package.
    Package is installed to c:\logstash. Path and binroot selection will be implemented in the next versions.
  
    This package is updated automatically to use new url when a new version comes out.
author: logstash
